		{"id":"883ca5fe1b712230","x":-300,"y":1540,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"Form Page"},
		{"id":"a0529521a1611692","x":-300,"y":1679,"width":250,"height":321,"type":"text","text":"Form Steps:\n\n- Choose verification method (BankID or Manual)\n- BankID mock / Manual identity fields\n- Contact details (Address, Zip, Phone, Email)\n- Terms & acceptance\n- Confirmation"},
		{"id":"579774365523b7ce","x":60,"y":1540,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"CSV Storage + Google sheets"},
		{"id":"3ec339bd76d245bf","x":-14,"y":1740,"width":398,"height":366,"type":"text","text":"- On form submit → your Next.js API route appends a row to Google Sheets via the **Google Sheets API** (service account, no OAuth needed for server-side writes)\n- The sheet acts as a live CRM the sales team can view in real time\n- Simultaneously write a local `/data/test-rides.csv` as backup (or for your future platform migration)\n- When your main motorcycle platform is ready, you swap the Sheets write for a REST call to your platform's API"},
		{"id":"6ff5fdb9fce5daef","x":60,"y":2273,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"Customer submits form"},
		{"id":"8302532a05d596c7","x":447,"y":2273,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"/api/test-ride/submit"},
